OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGovernment unveils new     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fextremism definition       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers have unveiled a new extremism
OL,6, definition under which certain groups  
OL,7, will be blocked from government funding
OL,8, or meeting officials.                  
OL,10,FIt will apply to, but not criminalise, 
OL,11,Fgroups that promote an ideology based  
OL,12,Fon "violence, hatred or intolerance".  
OL,14,FCommunities Secretary Michael Gove said
OL,15,Fa surge in extremism since the         
OL,16,FIsrael-Gaza war posed "a real risk" to 
OL,17,Fthe UK.                                
OL,19,FCivil liberties advocates, community   
OL,20,Fgroups and MPs have criticised recent  
OL,21,Fgovernment rhetoric on extremism.      
